You determine about your data.

Further information on data processing on our website and to our partners can be found in the Tracking data protection information.

We and our partners need your consent to use cookies and comparable technologies in our app and on our websites, unless they are already technically necessary to use the Vodafone website.

Analysis cookies serve to measure the use of our pages.

Usage profiles are created for personalization that further data can be assigned.

For data processing, data can also be transmitted to countries outside the EU/EEA whose data protection level does not correspond to that of the EU, e.g. in the USA.

net_feedback_terms_and_conditions_text:
I. Guarantee range and period

  1. The gigagary applies to Vodafone customers who have booked a mobile phone contract including data volume.
  2. The guarantee includes the provision of a data volume of 90 GB for the following 24 hours from the time of the customer feedback via the Meinvodafone app if the requirements below are met.
  3. The guarantee is made available by Vodafone at no additional costs.
  4. In the case of term contracts, the customer is informed of the Meinvodafone app as soon as the data volume of 90 GB has been activated.

II. Use of the guarantee

  1. In order to be able to use the guarantee, the customer sends his feedback on Vodafone via the Meinvodafone app.
  2. In order to be able to check the performance of the Vodafone network at the user on site based on the Vodafone's own network systems and to improve the Vodafone network for the user, Vodafone will evaluate personalized information on the network coverage and the quality of the data connections of the customer over the last 4 weeks from the time of feedback shipping.

III.

    The guarantee does not apply in the event of accidents, natural disasters and other causes that are neither controllable nor predictable by Vodafone, including, but not limited to lightning, water, fire, turmoil and inadequate ventilation and climate conditions.

IV. Compensation

This guarantee does not justify further claims, especially claims for damages.

V. Other

German law applies.

onboarding_3rd_party_permissions_descrip:
So that you can use our website and apps conveniently and see the personalized content for you, we use cookies, tags, pixels and similar technologies with your consent.

onboarding_bew_netperform_toggle_descrip:
What information do we get?

For example, we receive regular personalized information on the network coverage, the quality of your conversations and data connections, as well as the apps you use.

If you activate location services on your devices and support your operating system, we also collect information about your location such as your GPS coordinates or your radio cell.

We don't get any information about your conversation - or news content.

Your location data for better network

If you activate location services on your devices and support your operating system, we also collect information about your location, such as your GPS coordinates or your radio cell.

We use your personalized information, for example:

  • To give you more transparency about your personal data consumption,
  • to discover and fix any performance restrictions when using your apps or your smartphone,
  • To be specifically recommended for your tariff products & services.
